    "AngleOffset": "Offset from the main direction. The whole range is [main azimuth - angleOffset; main azimuth + angleOffset].",
    "AngleStep": "Determines the density of point placement between `Minimal angle` and `Maximal angle`. The angular distance between points. The number of points will be (`Maximal angle` - `Minimal angle`) / `AngleStep`.",
